get_pid - DERP OS man page

Name -------------------
get_pid() - return the id of the running process

Synopsis ---------------

#include "headers.h"

Status get_pid( Pid *pid );

Description ------------

The get_pid() function takes the running process and extracts the id. The id
is then stored into the pointer provided.

Return Value -----------

Upon successful return it will return SUCCESS

Errors -----------------

None
